{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_25","type":"agent_message","text":"现在已经足够确定改法了：最小 patch 不该去猜 thread process，而是单独给 `sendPrompt` 增一层“pending prompt”本地 UI state，再让 thread row / spotlight / running card 都从这层 state 读一个 `Queued` cue。最后只需要 host 在成功/失败时发一条轻量消息，不必立刻 full refresh。"}}
